CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 19, 1951, pg. 5, reads: "Four Generations - Mrs. Abraham Lincoln's family from Cleveland, Ohio, came over to be with her at the celebration... In the center is Mrs. Lincoln. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man and three women, including Mrs. Abraham Lincoln third from left posed in Trinity AME Church with other women and men in background
